•	Salt-
•	Sugar- one pinch
•	Extra virgin Olive Oil-1tsp
•	Pepper-pinch (opt)
METHOD:\n\n
1.	Peel your avocado and cut into desired shape ..U can cut either into cubes or slices .. \n
